    <h2>Meet the Graduate</h2>
<p>&quot;My experience on the TfL Graduate scheme has been positive, as it has allowed me the flexibility to explore many different parts of the company and work on a variety of interesting challenges, such as our School Party Travel Scheme, Commercial Reporting, machine learning projects in operational areas and process improvement. </p>
<p>I've learned a lot about all the different facets of a transport network from many different perspectives, all within a very supportive team of business analysts&quot;</p>
<p><strong>— Louisa, Technology Analyst Graduate</strong></p> 
