    <h2>Beyond the graduate scheme</h2>
<p>&quot;The TfL Graduate scheme proved an invaluable launchpad for my career. Over the course of two years I was given the accountability to deliver within high profile programmes including the roll out of Wi-Fi to London Underground stations and preparing the underpinning IT systems to support the new Elizabeth Line. The skills, knowledge and experience I obtained enable me to rise to the different challenges presented in an ever evolving technologically driven organisation.&quot;</p>
<p><strong>— Jamie, Technology Analyst Alumni</strong></p> 
 </div>
